- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is also a possible category as the paper discusses the worst-case running time of the proposed algorithm. 
- cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) is another possible category as the paper deals with the problem of finding common substrings in a discrete setting. 
- cs.CG (Computational Geometry) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with finding common substrings in a geometric sense (order-isomorphic substrings). 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper proposes an algorithm to solve a problem, which can be seen as a type of machine learning task.
